#.vscode/

# Flutter/Dart/Pub related
**/doc/api/
**/ios/Flutter/.last_build_id
.dart_tool/
# IMPORTANTE: NO excluir .flutter-plugins-dependencies
# Codemagic lo necesita para instalar los pods correctamente
# .flutter-plugins-dependencies
.pub-cache/
.pub/
/build/
/coverage/

# Symbolication related
app.*.symbols

# Obfuscation related
app.*.map.json

# Android Studio will place build artifacts here
/android/app/debug
/android/app/profile
/android/app/release

# Firebase - SEGURIDAD: no subir archivos con API keys al repositorio
# Descomenta estas líneas si tu repo es PÚBLICO
# google-services.json
# GoogleService-Info.plist

# iOS CocoaPods - no subir Pods (se regeneran con pod install)
ios/Pods/
ios/.symlinks/
ios/Podfile.lock

# iOS Flutter generados - contienen rutas absolutas locales del SO
# Codemagic los regenera con 'flutter pub get'
ios/Flutter/Generated.xcconfig
ios/Flutter/flutter_export_environment.sh
ios/Flutter/ephemeral/

